    <!-- SEO helper content -->
    <section class="card">
      <h2>About these calculators</h2>
      <p class="muted">These tools provide quick estimates to help guide your fitness journey. For medical concerns, consult a professional.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>BMI:</strong> A simple ratio of weight to height. It’s a screening tool, not a diagnosis.</li>
        <li><strong>Daily calories (TDEE):</strong> Based on BMR and activity. Your actual needs vary with training, body composition, and goals.</li>
